  "texts": [
    "Error analysis gives some important challenges the proposed framework, PolyNetDWTCADx faces in medical images: the features are visually quite similar between classes, and lesion shapes can be quite irregular.",
    "For instance, misclassifications in classes like polyp and hemorrhoid are on account of overlapping features; the model tries to surmount it by the DWT capability for refined feature extraction.",
    "Similarly, at the challenges of segmentation, like delineation of lesions with irregular shapes, the encoder-decoder architecture introduces skip connections in U-Net, preserving spatial and contextual information.",
    "Although there were some strengths in this methodology, a few classes that are underrepresented or complicated still have errors.",
    "Those will be discussed, proposing solutions by advanced augmentation techniques, like StyleGAN, and ensemble learning."
  ],
